<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p0.itc.cn/images01/20201128/07ab728f96034d678933e407c980dc07.jpeg" max-width="600"><span class="img-desc" style="font-size: 16px;">校友代表苏乐乐发言</span></img></p>
